        Expansive<br/>Human Futures
      </h1>
      <p class="vision-opening__lede">
        What "a future worth having" actually looks like.
      </p>
      <div class="vision-opening__body">
        <p>If AI could remake the world — or end it — the difference is what we build with it.</p>
        <p>We stand on the cusp of four revolutions, each as profound as anything in human history. Each one is a chance to flourish, or a chance to fail.</p>
        <p class="vision-opening__closer">This is our vision.</p>
      </div>
