  {# ============================================================
     SECTION A — SUPER-LONGEVITY
     Palette: warm amber / gold
     ============================================================ #}
  <section class="vision-pillar vision-pillar--longevity" id="longevity" aria-labelledby="longevity-heading">
    <div class="vision-pillar__backdrop" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="vision-container vision-pillar__grid">
      <header class="vision-pillar__head">
        <p class="vision-pillar__numeral">I</p>
        <h2 id="longevity-heading" class="vision-pillar__title">Super-Longevity</h2>
        <p class="vision-pillar__cusp">
          We stand on the cusp of medical revolutions as profound as the discovery of antibiotics.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="vision-pillar__body">
        <p>Two-thirds of deaths come from aging itself — heart disease, cancer, dementia, stroke.</p>
        <p>These are not fixed features of being human. They are problems, and they are becoming solvable.</p>
        <p class="vision-pillar__emphasis">
          A longer, healthier life is not a betrayal of faith — it is its fulfillment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="vision-scripture">
        <p class="vision-scripture__quote">
          &ldquo;Never again will there be an infant who lives but a few days, or an old man who does not live out his years.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <p class="vision-scripture__cite">Isaiah 65:20</p>
      </aside>

      <div class="vision-pillar__looks-like">
        <p class="vision-pillar__looks-label">What this looks like</p>
        <ul class="vision-pillar__list">
          <li>RNA medicines</li>
          <li>Senolytic drugs</li>
          <li>Bioprinted organs</li>
          <li>Shared genomic knowledge</li>
          <li>Screening for everyone, not just the wealthy</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="vision-pillar__deeper" href="/mission/technological/super-longevity/">
          Go deeper on Super-Longevity
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# ============================================================
     SECTION B — SUPER-EMBODIMENT
     Palette: deep red / crimson
     ============================================================ #}
  <section class="vision-pillar vision-pillar--embodiment" id="embodiment" aria-labelledby="embodiment-heading">
    <div class="vision-pillar__backdrop" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="vision-container vision-pillar__grid">
      <header class="vision-pillar__head">
        <p class="vision-pillar__numeral">II</p>
        <h2 id="embodiment-heading" class="vision-pillar__title">Super-Embodiment</h2>
        <p class="vision-pillar__cusp">
          We stand on the cusp of new ways to meet human needs for agency, connection, and creativity.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="vision-pillar__body">
        <p>"Go and tell John what you have seen: the blind receive their sight, the lame walk."</p>
        <p>The healing impulse at the heart of the gospel is now available in material form — brain-computer interfaces, gene therapy, assistive technology.</p>
        <p class="vision-pillar__emphasis">
          The question is not <em>whether</em> we'll enhance human life, but <em>whom we'll enhance it for</em>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="vision-scripture">
        <p class="vision-scripture__quote">
          &ldquo;Heal the sick, raise the dead, cure those with leprosy.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <p class="vision-scripture__cite">Matthew 10:8</p>
      </aside>

      <div class="vision-pillar__looks-like">
        <p class="vision-pillar__looks-label">What this looks like</p>
        <ul class="vision-pillar__list">
          <li>Brain-computer interfaces</li>
          <li>Gene therapy</li>
          <li>Assistive tech for the disabled first</li>
          <li>Enhancement governed by spiritual development, not status</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="vision-pillar__deeper" href="/mission/technological/super-embodiment/">
          Go deeper on Super-Embodiment
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# ============================================================
     SECTION C — SUPER-INTELLIGENCE
     Palette: electric blue / violet
     ============================================================ #}
  <section class="vision-pillar vision-pillar--intelligence" id="intelligence" aria-labelledby="intelligence-heading">
    <div class="vision-pillar__backdrop" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="vision-container vision-pillar__grid">
      <header class="vision-pillar__head">
        <p class="vision-pillar__numeral">III</p>
        <h2 id="intelligence-heading" class="vision-pillar__title">Super-Intelligence</h2>
        <p class="vision-pillar__cusp">
          We stand on the cusp of machine intelligence beyond our own — and new ways to expand our own.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="vision-pillar__body">
        <p>AI is here, AGI is coming, and the question is no longer <em>if</em> but <em>what values it carries</em>.</p>
        <p>We believe the answer is neither fear nor unchecked acceleration, but intelligence shaped by Christ — the Good Shepherd, the Wise King, the Suffering Servant, the compassionate heart of Mary.</p>
        <p class="vision-pillar__emphasis">
          If intelligence is the new substrate, then its ethical formation is the most urgent theological task of our time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="vision-scripture">
        <p class="vision-scripture__quote">
          &ldquo;This is eternal life, that we may know you, the only true God.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <p class="vision-scripture__cite">John 17:3</p>
      </aside>

      <div class="vision-pillar__looks-like">
        <p class="vision-pillar__looks-label">What this looks like</p>
        <ul class="vision-pillar__list">
          <li>Transparent AI development</li>
          <li>Christian ethical archetypes embedded in systems</li>
          <li>Human-AI hybrids with high ethical standards</li>
          <li>Loving enemies, even AI ones</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="vision-pillar__deeper" href="/mission/technological/super-intelligence/">
          Go deeper on Super-Intelligence
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# ============================================================
     SECTION D — SUPER-ECOLOGY
     Palette: green / teal
     ============================================================ #}
  <section class="vision-pillar vision-pillar--ecology" id="ecology" aria-labelledby="ecology-heading">
    <div class="vision-pillar__backdrop" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="vision-container vision-pillar__grid">
      <header class="vision-pillar__head">
        <p class="vision-pillar__numeral">IV</p>
        <h2 id="ecology-heading" class="vision-pillar__title">Super-Ecology</h2>
        <p class="vision-pillar__cusp">
          We stand on the cusp of radically expanded possibilities for cultivating life.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="vision-pillar__body">
        <p>The creation mandate was never "leave it alone." It was <em>cultivate</em>.</p>
        <p>The future renewal of creation will not revert to Eden — it will surpass it. Restore damaged ecosystems. Steward digital ones. Extend life, ethically, beyond Earth.</p>
        <p class="vision-pillar__emphasis">
          Build a world where privilege is not about resource access, but about what each of us chooses to do with superabundance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="vision-scripture">
        <p class="vision-scripture__quote">
          &ldquo;The creation waits in eager expectation&hellip;that it will be liberated from its bondage to decay.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <p class="vision-scripture__cite">Romans 8:19&ndash;21</p>
      </aside>

      <div class="vision-pillar__looks-like">
        <p class="vision-pillar__looks-label">What this looks like</p>
        <ul class="vision-pillar__list">
          <li>Ecological restoration</li>
          <li>Geoengineering by international agreement</li>
          <li>Digital ecologies that empower rather than exploit</li>
          <li>Habitats beyond Earth</li>
          <li>A politics of superabundance</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="vision-pillar__deeper" href="/mission/technological/super-ecology/">
          Go deeper on Super-Ecology
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

